RSP Implementation Committee. Ministry of Economic Affairs The Ministry\u201fs Economic Affairs Division hosts the Pakistan Development Forum, an annual event that provides an opportunity to review progress on aid effectiveness. A Donor Coordination Cell has been created to provide a single window for donor coordination and to ensure effective aid utilisation and management. Asia-Pacific Aid Effectiveness Portal February 2007 61 Pakistan Institute of Development Economics Established in Karachi in 1957, the Institute is devoted to theoretical and empirical research in Development Economics in general and on Pakistan-related economic issues in particular.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c9f60a53-6dde-4291-999a-06fe1aaae51c": {"__data__": {"id_": "c9f60a53-6dde-4291-999a-06fe1aaae51c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/getting-accra-information-portal-aid-effectiveness-asia-pacific-region", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Getting to Accra Information Portal on Aid Effectiveness for the Asia-Pacific Region", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/getting-accra-information-portal-aid-effectiveness-asia-pacific-region", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "0c44e9847d63d3216bbbb35bba63f577ecc0cd1a040526934048082a1f17ec73"}, "2": {"node_id": "88e18f46-f2c7-4fea-b0af-eea355fa970d", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/getting-accra-information-portal-aid-effectiveness-asia-pa